title: Orpalis PDF Reducer Professional v3.0.7
description:
Orpalis PDF Reducer Professional v3.0.7

PDF Reducer includes powerful, innovative and sophisticated features developed by worldwide recognized experts in document imaging.ORPALIS PDF Reducer is a super fast and powerful PDF compression Software for general public and developers meant to help anyone to get existing PDF files reduced up to 80% more than concurrent products.
To achieve that, ORPALIS PDF Reducer provides different innovative and highly sophisticated size-reducing techniques which can be optionally applied by user selection:

Nearly 100 input file formats
Multi-threading support
Command line interface support (for integrations or automations)
Unlimited batch processing
Content segmentation & optimal compression
Embedded raster images re-sampling & re-composition
Automatic color detection & layout analysis
Fast web view support (linearization)
Remove unwanted or unused objects
Drag & Drop support

Official Website: http://pdfreducer.orpalis.com/
